			<td><br>Gregory brings a broad base of telecommunications expertise, bridging technology development, marketing, sales and customer support, and business operations. Before joining Rayspan, he served as Director of Advanced Development and Product Definition for Kyocera handset business. His responsibilities spanned from simple component development to platform definition and demonstration. Gregory joined Kyocera in 2003 as Senior Manager of the antenna group, and he led the development of Kyocera's first internal antenna phone, with performance equal to that of external antenna phones. Gregory's academic credentials include a PhD in telecommunications from the University of Rennes, and an MBA from the Wharton School.</td>
